<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Stark1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Stark,</orth> adj. stiff (used only in speaking of a dead body): <cit><quote>lies s. and stiff,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.3.42" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 3, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>stiff and s. and cold,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 4.1.103" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 1, 103</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>how found you him? S., as you see,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.209" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 209</bibl></cit>.
